      "left": "0px",
      "text": "<b>בְּכוּלָּן</b> דכמהין ופטריות גידולי קרקע נינהו: <b>זומית.</b> שלמור\"א",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nedarim 55b:3:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        2
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "בלע\"ז: <b>אוֹמֵר ״שֶׁהַכֹּל <span class=\"dh-divergent\">נ&quot;ב</span>.</b> מדקא",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nedarim 55b:4:2",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        3
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "חשיב בכלל שאין גידולו מן הארץ",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nedarim 55b:4:2",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        3
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "כמהין ופטריות אלמא דלאו גידולי",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nedarim 55b:4:2",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        3
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "קרקע נינהו: <b>מֵאַוֵּירָא יָנְקִי.</b> שאין",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nedarim 55b:4:3",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        3
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "להם שרשים בארץ לפיכך אין מברכין",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nedarim 55b:4:3",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        3
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "עליהם כדבר שגדל מן הארץ: <b>וְהָא</b>",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nedarim 55b:4:4",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        3
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "<b>קָתָנֵי ״עַל דָּבָר שֶׁאֵין גִּידּוּלוֹ מִן הָאָרֶץ״.</b>",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nedarim 55b:4:4",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        3
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "והיינו כמהין ופטריות אלמא אפי'",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nedarim 55b:4:4",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        3
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "מירבא נמי לא רבו מארעא: <b>שֶׁאֵין</b>",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nedarim 55b:4:5",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        3
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "<b>יוֹנֵק</b> דהיינו כמהין ופטריות דמאוירא",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nedarim 55b:4:5",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        3
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "ינקי: <b>מַתְנִי׳ <span class=\"dh-divergent\">חמילה</span></b> כעין יריעה",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nedarim 55b:5:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        4
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "היא: <b>״קֻוֽנָּם צֶמֶר עוֹלֶה <span class=\"dh-divergent\">כו&#x27;</span></b> משמע",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nedarim 55b:5:2",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        4
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "מלבוש של צמר: <b>בַּאֲנִיצֵי פִּשְׁתָּן</b>",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nedarim 55b:5:3",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        4
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "דדייק ולא נפיץ: <b><span class=\"dh-divergent\">טעון</span> צֶמֶר. <span class=\"dh-divergent\">ופשתן</span></b>",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nedarim 55b:6:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        5
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "<b>וְהִזִּיעַ</b> מחמת המשוי: והיה ריחו",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nedarim 55b:6:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        5
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "קשה וכו': <b>וְאָסוּר <span class=\"dh-divergent\">להפשילן</span> לַאֲחוֹרָיו.</b>",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nedarim 55b:6:3",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        5
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "לעשות משוי מאותן מינין דבענין",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nedarim 55b:6:3",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        5
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "שנצטער נדר דהיינו לטעון ולא לכסות",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nedarim 55b:6:3",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        5
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "ולהכי מותר לכסות: <b>גְּמָ׳ <span class=\"dh-divergent\">פונדא</span></b>",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nedarim 55b:7:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        6
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "אזור חלול שחוגרין בו: <b>פסקיא</b>",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nedarim 55b:7:2",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        6
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "פיישול\"א: <b>אסקורטיא</b> מפרש לקמן:",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nedarim 55b:7:3",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        6
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "<b>קטבליא</b> מלבוש של עור קשה",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nedarim 55b:7:4",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        6
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "שלובש על האסקורטיא: <b><span class=\"dh-divergent\">אנפליא</span></b>",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nedarim 55b:7:5",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        6
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "הוש\"ש בלע\"ז של עור: <b><span class=\"dh-divergent\">פליניא</span></b>",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nedarim 55b:7:6",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        6
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "סינר: <b>כִּיתּוּנָא דְצַלָּא</b> מלבוש של עור:",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nedarim 55b:7:7",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        6
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "<b><span class=\"dh-divergent\">סגוס</span> עָבֶה.</b> מין שק הוא עבה טפי",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nedarim 55b:8:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        7
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "מיריעה: יוצאין בשבת -בכל אלו",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nedarim 55b:8:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        7
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "דברים: <b>אֲבָל לֹא בְּתֵיבָה</b> שלא יכוף",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nedarim 55b:8:3",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        7
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "תיבה על ראשו ויצא דמשוי הוי: <b>וּמוּתָּר</b>",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nedarim 55b:9:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        8
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "<b>לִטְעוֹן</b> שלא נדר אלא ממלבוש שהרי",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nedarim 55b:9:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        8
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "היה מצטער ממלבוש: <b>וְהִזִּיעַ</b> מכובד",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nedarim 55b:9:2",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        8
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "משוי: <b>וְאָסוּר לִטְעוֹן.</b> שלא נדר אלא כפי",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nedarim 55b:9:3",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        8
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "שהצר לו המשוי הילכך מותר ללבוש:",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nedarim 55b:9:3",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        8
      ]
    }
  ],
  "tosafot": [
    {
      "width": "450px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "מה שנ\"ל ודברי הרמב\"ם ז\"ל אינם כן בפ\"ח מהלכות"
    },
    {
      "width": "400px",
      "right": "50px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "נדרים"
    },
    {
      "width": "450px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": ""
    },
    {
      "width": "450px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "(הלכה"
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": ""
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": ""
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": ""
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": ""
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": ""
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "ח). <b><span class=\"dh-divergent\">חילקא</span></b> </big>.</b> חטין כתושין",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Nedarim 55b:2:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        1
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "חלוקין לשנים: <b><span class=\"dh-divergent\">טרגיס</span></b> </big>.</b> חד לתלתא:",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Nedarim 55b:2:2",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        1
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "<b>טיסני.</b> </big>.</b> חד",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Nedarim 55b:2:3",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        1
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Nedarim 55b:2:3",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        1
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "לארבעה: <big><b>אָסוּר בְּכוּלָּן.</b> דכמיהין",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Nedarim 55b:2:4",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        1
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "ופטריות",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Nedarim 55b:2:4",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        1
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "בכלל גדולי",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Nedarim 55b:2:4",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        1
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "קרקע הן:",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Nedarim 55b:2:4",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        1
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "<big><b>מִירְבָּא רָבוּ</b>",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Nedarim 55b:4:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        3
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "<b>מֵאַרְעָא.</b> כמהין ופטריות",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Nedarim 55b:4:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        3
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "ודאי מארעא רבו ושפיר מיקרו",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Nedarim 55b:4:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        3
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "גידולי קרקע",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Nedarim 55b:4:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        3
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "אבל היניקה",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Nedarim 55b:4:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        3
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "שלהם אינה אלא מאויר",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Nedarim 55b:4:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        3
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "קרקע",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Nedarim 55b:4:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        3
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "ולא",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Nedarim 55b:4:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        3
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "מברכין",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Nedarim 55b:4:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        3
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "בורא",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Nedarim 55b:4:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        3
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "פרי האדמה: <big><b><span class=\"dh-divergent\">שק</span></b></big>",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Nedarim 55b:5:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        4
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "<big><b><span class=\"dh-divergent\">יריעה</span> <span class=\"dh-divergent\">וחמילה</span>.</b> אינן",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Nedarim 55b:5:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        4
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Nedarim 55b:5:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        4
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Nedarim 55b:5:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        4
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "בגדים הם: <big><b>מוּתָּר</b></big>",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Nedarim 55b:6:3",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        5
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "<b>לְהִתְכַּסּוֹת בְּגִיזֵּי צֶמֶר.</b> שלא",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Nedarim 55b:6:3",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        5
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "נתכוון זה אלא לבגד ארוג:",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Nedarim 55b:6:3",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        5
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "<big><b>הכל לפי הנודר.</b> פירוש"
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "לפי ענין"
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "שהיה בשעת הנדר:"
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": ""
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "<big><b>היה טעון.</b>"
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "פירוש"
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "מופשל"
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "לאחוריו כדרך נושאי"
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "משאות:"
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "<big><b>מותר.</b></big>"
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "<b>להתכסות.</b> שלא"
    },
    {
      "width": "930px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "נתכוון לאסור אלא"
    },
    {
      "width": "930px",
